B-side of My Hero single (in UK)  
  Baker Street  
  
  *To get the feel of the strumming and solos etc.. you should listen*  
  *to the song, I know it was released as a B-side to the My Hero single*  
  *in the UK, I don't know about releases in America though.*  
  *All chords are power chords, except during the verse, and the minor*  
  *chords. You can also try picking the Dm and Am chords at the beginning of*  
  *the chorus if you have two guitars, for a nice effect.*  
  *The chorus can also be played with Dm7 and Am7, but I don't think it*  
  *sounds right like that.*  
  
  *Chords used:*  
     *EADGBe*  
