  ***G***  [355xxx]  
  ***A***  [577xxx]  
  ***C***  [x355xxx]  
  ***D***  [x577xx]  
  
  *Key:*  
  *10b   - Bend note*  
  *13h   - Hammer-on*  
  *12p   - Pull-off*  
  *13/10 - Slide to next note*  
  *10~~~ - Hold note*  
  *(7)   - Ghost note, don't necessarily play it*  
  *(x12) - Play 12 times*  
  
