Watershed  
  
  *This song is another pretty much straight forward song. There are a*  
  *couple things to keep in mind. First, when it gets to the bridge (I*  
  *want to swim in a watershed) the song switches from 4/4 to 7/4 time;*  
  *that is, a measure of 4/4 and a measure of 3/4. The bridge is right,*  
  *I think, but I think there is some effect that Dave uses on riffs like*  
  *those that makes a single note sound like a whole chord, which I don't*  
  *think is chorus, but it might be.*  
  
