X-Static  
  
  *This song is one of the less complex songs on the album, with only two*  
  *main parts, but the 2 guitars can get a little tricky. One clean-*  
  *sounding guitar starts the intro with it's part, then the 2nd guitar*  
  *starts playing over it, giving it a harmonizing effect (which for some*  
  *reason seems to remind me of Soundgarden.)*  
  *It's all pretty simple.*  
  
